1
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:26,300
♪The gentle breeze leaves no trace♪

2
00:00:26,300 --> 00:00:29,670
♪It stirs the old times♪

3
00:00:30,240 --> 00:00:33,560
♪Love is gained and lost♪

4
00:00:33,560 --> 00:00:37,370
♪Only then does it become unforgettable♪

5
00:00:37,720 --> 00:00:41,370
♪The bamboo leaves
are rustling and falling♪

6
00:00:41,370 --> 00:00:44,770
♪Fate is delayed and scattered♪

7
00:00:45,050 --> 00:00:48,840
♪Only lingering hatred remains♪

8
00:00:48,840 --> 00:00:51,210
♪Echoing♪

9
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:55,130
♪Old dreams are like illusions♪

10
00:00:55,320 --> 00:00:59,490
♪Alas, the world is too indifferent♪

11
00:00:59,490 --> 00:01:01,760
♪If there were no obsession♪

12
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:05,870
♪I wouldn't be thinking of someone♪

13
00:01:06,320 --> 00:01:09,630
♪If it's destined to be alone♪

14
00:01:09,630 --> 00:01:13,310
♪Like a snowstorm♪

15
00:01:13,710 --> 00:01:15,980
♪When love and hate dissolve♪

16
00:01:15,980 --> 00:01:20,940
♪Only a long gaze remains♪

17
00:01:21,140 --> 00:01:25,610
♪A drop of tear♪

18
00:01:25,610 --> 00:01:29,490
♪Falls, burning my heart♪

19
00:01:29,490 --> 00:01:33,340
♪We loved without regret♪

20
00:01:33,340 --> 00:01:36,580
=My Destined Consort=

21
00:01:36,660 --> 00:01:39,660
=Episode 16=

22
00:01:42,210 --> 00:01:43,050
Mr. Chu,

23
00:01:43,570 --> 00:01:44,770
I've picked a gift for you.

24
00:01:45,260 --> 00:01:46,930
Thank you for healing my scar.

25
00:01:47,690 --> 00:01:48,690
I've put it here for you.

26
00:02:08,290 --> 00:02:09,690
You travel far and wide

27
00:02:09,690 --> 00:02:11,100
for the people of the world.

28
00:02:12,100 --> 00:02:13,170
I hope

29
00:02:13,450 --> 00:02:15,170
this small water pouch

30
00:02:15,610 --> 00:02:17,610
can provide you with some comfort

31
00:02:17,610 --> 00:02:18,730
during your long journeys.

32
00:02:26,690 --> 00:02:27,530
Qilan.

33
00:02:29,290 --> 00:02:30,730
Here, try this.

34
00:02:31,890 --> 00:02:32,850
It's prepared for you.

35
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:35,160
If you like sour food,
it means it's a boy.

36
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:35,700
Eat more.

37
00:02:38,980 --> 00:02:39,820
It's delicious.

38
00:02:40,940 --> 00:02:41,780
It's a boy.

39
00:02:42,380 --> 00:02:43,340
Come on. Eat up.

40
00:02:45,780 --> 00:02:46,980
Here, try this.

41
00:02:50,340 --> 00:02:51,180
Try this.

42
00:02:55,460 --> 00:02:56,330
Qilan.

43
00:02:56,700 --> 00:02:58,060
Eat more fruit.

44
00:02:58,180 --> 00:03:00,100
The braised pork is
Master Jingxiu's favorite.

45
00:03:00,100 --> 00:03:01,020
Let him eat it.

46
00:03:01,180 --> 00:03:02,980
It's just braised pork.

47
00:03:03,580 --> 00:03:04,420
Danling,

48
00:03:04,420 --> 00:03:05,540
the way you're speaking now

49
00:03:05,540 --> 00:03:07,180
is becoming more inappropriate.

50
00:03:08,860 --> 00:03:10,740
Sorry for speaking out of turn.

51
00:03:11,460 --> 00:03:12,300
It's okay.

52
00:03:16,020 --> 00:03:16,860
Lady Lan,

53
00:03:17,020 --> 00:03:18,300
the antiabortifacient is ready.

54
00:03:18,310 --> 00:03:19,930
Qilan, drink it while it's hot.

55
00:03:22,820 --> 00:03:24,080
Be careful not to burn yourself.

56
00:03:28,380 --> 00:03:29,780
Master Jingxiu, you eat too.

57
00:03:30,260 --> 00:03:31,100
No rush.

58
00:03:38,510 --> 00:03:39,360
Try this.

59
00:03:42,940 --> 00:03:44,140
My son will surely like this,

60
00:03:44,340 --> 00:03:45,180
just like me.

61
00:03:51,860 --> 00:03:52,740
What's wrong?

62
00:03:55,610 --> 00:03:57,180
- What's wrong?
- What's wrong, Qilan?

63
00:03:57,700 --> 00:03:58,540
My belly...

64
00:03:58,550 --> 00:03:59,490
Your belly?

65
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:00,340
Qilan.

66
00:04:00,820 --> 00:04:02,100
- I didn't.
- My belly...

67
00:04:03,260 --> 00:04:04,580
Call the physician!

68
00:04:04,580 --> 00:04:05,420
Yes.

69
00:04:07,380 --> 00:04:08,220
Qilan...

70
00:04:20,820 --> 00:04:21,660
How is it?

71
00:04:22,140 --> 00:04:23,740
How is the baby?

72
00:04:26,580 --> 00:04:27,420
Lady Wang,

73
00:04:28,180 --> 00:04:29,020
Master Jingxiu,

74
00:04:29,580 --> 00:04:31,260
I'm afraid

75
00:04:31,260 --> 00:04:32,100
Lady Lan

76
00:04:32,660 --> 00:04:33,620
had a miscarriage.

77
00:04:35,700 --> 00:04:37,040
- What?
- What?

78
00:04:38,780 --> 00:04:39,620
What?

79
00:04:40,860 --> 00:04:41,700
Consort Danling...

80
00:04:44,140 --> 00:04:45,700
Consort Danling, why harm me?

81
00:04:47,100 --> 00:04:48,220
What are you saying?

82
00:04:48,780 --> 00:04:50,180
How could I harm you?

83
00:04:50,580 --> 00:04:51,700
I was fine.

84
00:04:53,180 --> 00:04:55,260
Why did I lose the child after taking

85
00:04:55,780 --> 00:04:57,100
your antiabortifacient?

86
00:04:57,300 --> 00:04:58,140
Yes.

87
00:04:58,980 --> 00:05:00,340
Qilan drank your medicine

88
00:05:00,340 --> 00:05:01,500
and had a miscarriage.

89
00:05:01,700 --> 00:05:02,820
What exactly happened?

90
00:05:03,060 --> 00:05:03,900
Master Jingxiu,

91
00:05:04,100 --> 00:05:05,380
I'm innocent.

92
00:05:05,740 --> 00:05:06,860
How could I be foolish enough

93
00:05:07,180 --> 00:05:09,100
to poison her in front of everyone?

94
00:05:15,460 --> 00:05:16,420
Shen Qilan,

95
00:05:17,140 --> 00:05:18,620
I've treated you with so much care.

96
00:05:18,820 --> 00:05:20,340
Why repay me with hatred

97
00:05:20,340 --> 00:05:21,660
and frame me like this?

98
00:05:26,620 --> 00:05:27,980
That's not true, Lady Wang.

99
00:05:28,620 --> 00:05:29,460
Consort Danling

100
00:05:29,580 --> 00:05:31,500
has always disliked Lady Lan.

101
00:05:31,900 --> 00:05:32,900
Not long ago,

102
00:05:33,380 --> 00:05:35,100
she made Lady Lan kneel
until she fainted,

103
00:05:35,380 --> 00:05:37,420
claiming it was the rule.

104
00:05:38,220 --> 00:05:39,060
Outrageous!

105
00:05:39,660 --> 00:05:40,920
You have no place to speak here.

106
00:05:48,580 --> 00:05:49,420
Master Jingxiu,

107
00:05:49,980 --> 00:05:50,820
Mother,

108
00:05:52,700 --> 00:05:53,940
she's twisting the truth.

109
00:05:54,180 --> 00:05:55,140
Don't believe her.

110
00:05:55,580 --> 00:05:56,900
I'm not twisting the truth.

111
00:05:57,140 --> 00:05:58,490
Lady Wang, if you don't believe me,

112
00:05:58,780 --> 00:06:00,770
you can ask the other servants
in the mansion.

113
00:06:02,100 --> 00:06:02,940
I...

114
00:06:04,380 --> 00:06:05,230
Qilan.

115
00:06:05,230 --> 00:06:06,980
- I've always been careful.
- Qilan.

116
00:06:07,620 --> 00:06:09,340
I've been careful with my food.

117
00:06:10,500 --> 00:06:11,460
Consort Danling

118
00:06:12,380 --> 00:06:14,500
brought the antiabortifacient to me.

119
00:06:15,380 --> 00:06:16,220
Mother,

120
00:06:16,220 --> 00:06:18,060
you have to stand up for me.

121
00:06:20,940 --> 00:06:22,180
Please believe me.

122
00:06:22,740 --> 00:06:24,060
Don't walk into others' traps.

123
00:06:26,140 --> 00:06:26,980
In that case,

124
00:06:27,540 --> 00:06:28,900
bring the private physician here.

125
00:06:29,940 --> 00:06:31,100
Whether you've poisoned her

126
00:06:31,620 --> 00:06:32,620
will be clear then.

127
00:06:33,420 --> 00:06:34,260
Yes.

128
00:06:41,700 --> 00:06:42,860
My child...

129
00:06:44,100 --> 00:06:48,900
(Master Jingxiu's Mansion)

130
00:06:57,580 --> 00:06:58,580
Jingxiu, don't worry.

131
00:06:59,260 --> 00:07:00,540
This physician is the one

132
00:07:00,540 --> 00:07:02,140
who normally treats your father.

133
00:07:02,620 --> 00:07:04,420
I've invited him today

134
00:07:04,420 --> 00:07:05,460
to find out

135
00:07:06,020 --> 00:07:08,100
who wanted my grandson's life.

136
00:07:10,380 --> 00:07:11,300
Lady Wang,

137
00:07:11,300 --> 00:07:12,140
Master Jingming,

138
00:07:12,580 --> 00:07:13,700
someone altered the formula

139
00:07:13,700 --> 00:07:15,820
for Lady Lan's antiabortifacient,

140
00:07:16,220 --> 00:07:18,540
turning it into an antiabortifacient,

141
00:07:18,820 --> 00:07:20,300
causing Qilan to miscarry.

142
00:07:21,580 --> 00:07:22,900
You've always been in charge

143
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:24,460
of Qilan's antiabortifacient.

144
00:07:24,850 --> 00:07:26,420
The physician has said so.

145
00:07:27,060 --> 00:07:28,460
What can you say in your defense?

146
00:07:28,660 --> 00:07:29,500
Mother,

147
00:07:30,300 --> 00:07:31,580
are you suspecting me?

148
00:07:33,460 --> 00:07:34,340
It's not me.

149
00:07:39,620 --> 00:07:40,780
Master Jingxiu, believe me.

150
00:07:41,020 --> 00:07:41,900
How could I

151
00:07:41,900 --> 00:07:43,060
harm your child?

152
00:07:43,820 --> 00:07:44,660
Master Jingxiu...

153
00:07:47,180 --> 00:07:48,020
Fine.

154
00:07:49,020 --> 00:07:50,540
Then explain to us

155
00:07:51,460 --> 00:07:52,580
what happened.

156
00:07:54,060 --> 00:07:55,420
- I...
- It was me.

157
00:07:55,700 --> 00:07:57,220
Lady Wang, Young Master,

158
00:07:57,620 --> 00:07:59,520
- It was me.
- You have no place to speak here!

159
00:08:04,420 --> 00:08:05,260
Speak!

160
00:08:08,540 --> 00:08:09,500
I had increased

161
00:08:11,340 --> 00:08:13,060
the dosage of the antiabortifacient.

162
00:08:13,620 --> 00:08:15,060
But I only wanted

163
00:08:15,420 --> 00:08:16,660
to make the baby stronger

164
00:08:16,660 --> 00:08:18,020
so I added more.

165
00:08:19,060 --> 00:08:20,740
I checked the dosage with a physician.

166
00:08:21,060 --> 00:08:22,460
Nothing should've gone wrong.

167
00:08:23,660 --> 00:08:24,820
It must be Shen Qilan.

168
00:08:24,820 --> 00:08:26,100
She must've eaten something bad

169
00:08:26,220 --> 00:08:27,640
and framed me with the miscarriage.

170
00:08:28,260 --> 00:08:29,460
I see.

171
00:08:29,620 --> 00:08:31,100
Lady Lan's pulse

172
00:08:31,260 --> 00:08:32,260
tells me she's weak.

173
00:08:32,540 --> 00:08:33,540
With that dosage,

174
00:08:33,700 --> 00:08:35,420
she'd surely have a miscarriage.

175
00:08:35,980 --> 00:08:37,540
What more do you have to say?

176
00:08:38,380 --> 00:08:39,420
You poisonous woman!

177
00:08:39,820 --> 00:08:41,660
This is the Prefect's eldest grandson!

178
00:08:44,140 --> 00:08:44,980
Mother,

179
00:08:45,580 --> 00:08:47,260
I meant well.

180
00:08:47,940 --> 00:08:50,140
I could never harm
Master Jingxiu's child!

181
00:08:51,860 --> 00:08:53,180
Let the physician leave.

182
00:08:54,380 --> 00:08:55,220
Lady Wang,

183
00:08:55,860 --> 00:08:56,700
Master Jingxiu,

184
00:08:57,340 --> 00:08:58,300
this

185
00:08:58,700 --> 00:08:59,620
is of great importance.

186
00:08:59,820 --> 00:09:00,940
I dare not hide anything.

187
00:09:01,340 --> 00:09:03,120
I will report it truthfully
to the Prefect.

188
00:09:10,860 --> 00:09:12,460
Master Jingxiu, Lady Wang,

189
00:09:12,620 --> 00:09:13,580
I beg you.

190
00:09:13,860 --> 00:09:15,820
Please be fair to Lady Lan.

191
00:09:16,860 --> 00:09:17,740
These days,

192
00:09:18,520 --> 00:09:21,140
Consort Danling has been
making things hard for her.

193
00:09:21,780 --> 00:09:23,860
She had to review the ledgers
late at night

194
00:09:23,880 --> 00:09:25,980
and would be punished
even for the slightest mistake.

195
00:09:25,980 --> 00:09:26,840
I didn't.

196
00:09:26,850 --> 00:09:29,060
- She had to kneel on the abacus.
- I didn't.

197
00:09:29,940 --> 00:09:32,500
As a maid, even I couldn't handle it.

198
00:09:32,860 --> 00:09:35,040
Lady Lan was even pregnant.

199
00:09:35,780 --> 00:09:37,540
- And this antiabortifacient.
- I didn't.

200
00:09:37,820 --> 00:09:39,100
Consort Danling

201
00:09:39,100 --> 00:09:40,420
must've plotted

202
00:09:40,820 --> 00:09:42,540
to cause this miscarriage.

203
00:09:43,180 --> 00:09:44,460
Is this true?

204
00:09:44,660 --> 00:09:45,500
Mother,

205
00:09:45,980 --> 00:09:47,320
please don't believe her nonsense.

206
00:09:48,180 --> 00:09:49,620
Shen Qilan begged me.

207
00:09:49,900 --> 00:09:51,060
She asked me to teach her

208
00:09:51,660 --> 00:09:52,880
how to manage the household

209
00:09:53,380 --> 00:09:54,740
so I agreed.

210
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:57,220
I never expected her
to twist my intentions,

211
00:09:58,860 --> 00:10:00,540
accusing me of targeting her.

212
00:10:01,020 --> 00:10:02,740
She's overestimated herself.

213
00:10:03,940 --> 00:10:06,420
She's a concubine's daughter
from a humble family.

214
00:10:06,420 --> 00:10:08,220
So what if she has a child?

215
00:10:09,060 --> 00:10:10,740
Even without a child,

216
00:10:10,740 --> 00:10:12,500
I'm still the general's lineal daughter

217
00:10:12,740 --> 00:10:13,900
and Master Jingxiu's wife.

218
00:10:14,660 --> 00:10:16,200
Why should I bother to plot against her?

219
00:10:17,380 --> 00:10:18,780
I think what happened today

220
00:10:18,780 --> 00:10:20,300
is part of her plan to play the victim

221
00:10:21,020 --> 00:10:22,180
and frame me.

222
00:10:23,260 --> 00:10:24,380
Are you saying

223
00:10:24,630 --> 00:10:26,820
she used her child to frame me?

224
00:10:27,380 --> 00:10:28,940
What kind of mother

225
00:10:28,940 --> 00:10:30,860
would risk her child's life?

226
00:10:31,180 --> 00:10:32,020
Mother,

227
00:10:32,460 --> 00:10:33,300
you don't understand.

228
00:10:34,460 --> 00:10:35,700
Women of low birth

229
00:10:35,700 --> 00:10:36,980
like her

230
00:10:37,460 --> 00:10:38,860
often pretend to be subservient.

231
00:10:39,140 --> 00:10:40,560
She's known since she was young

232
00:10:40,560 --> 00:10:42,600
that she had to suffer
to get something better.

233
00:10:44,510 --> 00:10:45,380
My child...

234
00:10:45,380 --> 00:10:46,220
Qilan...

235
00:10:49,900 --> 00:10:50,740
Qilan, I'm here.

236
00:10:52,180 --> 00:10:53,060
My child...

237
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:58,140
Master Jingxiu.

238
00:11:00,540 --> 00:11:01,380
Master Jingxiu,

239
00:11:02,220 --> 00:11:03,780
I just dreamed about our child.

240
00:11:04,780 --> 00:11:06,060
He looked adorable,

241
00:11:07,740 --> 00:11:09,940
just like you.

242
00:11:11,500 --> 00:11:12,340
Our child

243
00:11:12,980 --> 00:11:14,100
was so smart.

244
00:11:14,540 --> 00:11:16,580
He could call us at a young age.

245
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:18,240
I also dreamed...

246
00:11:18,500 --> 00:11:20,020
I dreamed that our child

247
00:11:20,340 --> 00:11:21,620
loved his grandparents.

248
00:11:22,300 --> 00:11:23,780
When the Prefect held him,

249
00:11:23,940 --> 00:11:25,580
he grabbed the Prefect's beard

250
00:11:25,820 --> 00:11:27,700
and made the Prefect laugh.

251
00:11:28,020 --> 00:11:29,060
The Prefect said

252
00:11:29,060 --> 00:11:30,100
he was the eldest grandson,

253
00:11:30,260 --> 00:11:31,220
his eldest grandson.

254
00:11:31,620 --> 00:11:33,340
Qilan, we will have more children.

255
00:11:34,860 --> 00:11:37,180
I didn't see him grow up.

256
00:11:37,900 --> 00:11:40,180
I didn't see him study or practice

257
00:11:40,180 --> 00:11:42,180
martial arts with you.

258
00:11:44,260 --> 00:11:46,220
I didn't even let him help me

259
00:11:46,860 --> 00:11:48,580
solve your problems.

260
00:11:49,260 --> 00:11:51,100
Now, Master Jingxiu,

261
00:11:52,140 --> 00:11:53,620
I've never even heard him

262
00:11:53,620 --> 00:11:55,860
call me Mother.

263
00:11:56,140 --> 00:11:56,980
Qilan...

264
00:12:04,300 --> 00:12:05,140
Master Jingxiu,

265
00:12:06,540 --> 00:12:07,980
I really don't know

266
00:12:08,580 --> 00:12:09,900
how this happened.

267
00:12:11,700 --> 00:12:12,780
Even if there was a mistake,

268
00:12:13,420 --> 00:12:14,740
it was unintentional.

269
00:12:16,020 --> 00:12:17,460
Please forgive me, Master Jingxiu.

270
00:12:18,100 --> 00:12:19,540
Stop defending yourself.

271
00:12:20,140 --> 00:12:22,280
If it weren't for your jealousy
over Qilan's pregnancy

272
00:12:22,620 --> 00:12:24,300
and your dirty tricks,

273
00:12:24,820 --> 00:12:26,780
how could I lose my grandson?

274
00:12:27,820 --> 00:12:29,180
Even if your father

275
00:12:29,410 --> 00:12:30,890
knows about this,

276
00:12:31,170 --> 00:12:32,620
he can't defend you.

277
00:12:33,980 --> 00:12:34,820
Jingxiu,

278
00:12:35,300 --> 00:12:37,340
you can't forgive her.

279
00:12:41,580 --> 00:12:42,420
Qilan,

280
00:12:43,620 --> 00:12:44,540
rest well.

281
00:13:02,660 --> 00:13:04,700
How could it be unintentional?

282
00:13:06,100 --> 00:13:06,940
Today,

283
00:13:09,460 --> 00:13:12,140
I'll strip you of your position
as my consort.

284
00:13:12,700 --> 00:13:13,740
In three days,

285
00:13:14,220 --> 00:13:15,690
you will be sent to the ancestral tomb

286
00:13:17,070 --> 00:13:18,620
to reflect on your mistakes.

287
00:13:24,980 --> 00:13:25,980
Master Jingxiu,

288
00:13:27,740 --> 00:13:29,220
you're abandoning me?

289
00:13:31,900 --> 00:13:33,700
I'm your wife,

