00:27:09,860 --> 00:27:10,700
Jiangli,

579
00:27:12,140 --> 00:27:13,060
this is

580
00:27:13,060 --> 00:27:15,140
the Lantian jade bracelet
from Master Jingxiu.

581
00:27:15,580 --> 00:27:17,580
This jade is rare and valuable,

582
00:27:17,940 --> 00:27:20,060
and it perfectly matches
your noble demeanor.

583
00:27:20,500 --> 00:27:22,540
Please allow me

584
00:27:23,060 --> 00:27:25,140
to give this to you.

585
00:27:29,820 --> 00:27:30,660
You should

586
00:27:30,980 --> 00:27:32,260
keep it for yourself.

587
00:27:33,540 --> 00:27:35,180
The inner chambers are eerie.

588
00:27:36,780 --> 00:27:38,180
One slight mistake

589
00:27:38,340 --> 00:27:39,780
might make you fall into hell

590
00:27:40,820 --> 00:27:41,820
like Wang Danling.

591
00:27:43,700 --> 00:27:44,620
This bracelet

592
00:27:45,340 --> 00:27:46,620
will help protect you from evil.

593
00:27:48,780 --> 00:27:49,820
You're right.

594
00:27:50,780 --> 00:27:52,500
We can't harbor malicious intent

595
00:27:52,820 --> 00:27:54,020
like her,

596
00:27:55,100 --> 00:27:57,540
but people have many helpless moments.

597
00:27:57,940 --> 00:27:59,710
Sometimes, it's just
to protect themselves.

598
00:28:00,220 --> 00:28:01,140
Jiangli, do you agree?

599
00:28:06,600 --> 00:28:08,900
It's never wrong
to consider yourself first.

600
00:28:09,720 --> 00:28:10,860
But people live only once.

601
00:28:11,660 --> 00:28:12,600
Some things can be done,

602
00:28:13,100 --> 00:28:14,040
but some things can't.

603
00:28:17,060 --> 00:28:18,660
We must stick to our bottom line.

604
00:28:22,620 --> 00:28:24,380
I'll follow your advice.

605
00:28:25,460 --> 00:28:27,100
I don't have any advice for you.

606
00:28:28,460 --> 00:28:30,060
Where is Wang Danling now?

607
00:28:31,500 --> 00:28:33,100
She's under house arrest in her room.

608
00:28:33,340 --> 00:28:34,740
Are you going to see her?

609
00:28:35,460 --> 00:28:37,860
We've had many entanglements for years.

610
00:28:38,260 --> 00:28:39,260
Now that she's leaving,

611
00:28:39,900 --> 00:28:40,980
I should go see her.

612
00:28:43,900 --> 00:28:44,980
Rest well.

613
00:28:46,100 --> 00:28:47,040
No need to see me off.

614
00:28:51,900 --> 00:28:52,740
Jiangli, take care.

615
00:29:22,100 --> 00:29:23,220
What are you here for?

616
00:29:24,500 --> 00:29:25,660
I came to see you.

617
00:29:27,380 --> 00:29:29,340
Are you here to laugh at me?

618
00:29:30,180 --> 00:29:31,380
Let me tell you.

619
00:29:32,340 --> 00:29:33,460
I'm doing just fine.

620
00:29:37,060 --> 00:29:38,860
Stop playing tough now.

621
00:29:40,070 --> 00:29:42,100
Still dreaming about becoming
the Prefect's wife?

622
00:29:46,340 --> 00:29:47,940
Who are you to laugh at me?

623
00:29:49,220 --> 00:29:50,660
Even if I'm not a consort anymore,

624
00:29:52,500 --> 00:29:54,020
I'm still the general's only daughter.

625
00:29:55,180 --> 00:29:56,020
I'm not you.

626
00:29:57,350 --> 00:29:58,620
You marrying Master Jingming

627
00:30:00,410 --> 00:30:02,380
can even be considered rarely lucky.

628
00:30:05,660 --> 00:30:07,620
Do you think your marriage

629
00:30:08,140 --> 00:30:10,160
can make you my equal?

630
00:30:11,060 --> 00:30:12,060
You don't deserve it!

631
00:30:13,470 --> 00:30:15,040
Someone as insignificant as me

632
00:30:15,670 --> 00:30:18,060
could still become your thorn
in the side

633
00:30:18,580 --> 00:30:20,500
and the target of your schemes
again and again.

634
00:30:21,300 --> 00:30:22,380
I don't even know

635
00:30:22,380 --> 00:30:23,580
whether I should feel sad

636
00:30:24,260 --> 00:30:25,290
or proud.

637
00:30:25,880 --> 00:30:26,980
I don't even know what I did

638
00:30:26,980 --> 00:30:28,180
to offend you.

639
00:30:29,020 --> 00:30:30,060
It was you who chose

640
00:30:30,060 --> 00:30:31,500
to marry Master Jingxiu,

641
00:30:32,500 --> 00:30:34,560
but to achieve your goals,
you plotted against me.

642
00:30:34,740 --> 00:30:36,340
I hadn't even sought revenge on you,

643
00:30:36,940 --> 00:30:38,340
yet you made things hard for me

644
00:30:38,820 --> 00:30:40,180
because I married Master Jingming.

645
00:30:40,780 --> 00:30:42,580
Don't you think you're too overbearing?

646
00:30:45,340 --> 00:30:46,180
Overbearing?

647
00:30:47,100 --> 00:30:48,300
You should know this.

648
00:30:49,300 --> 00:30:51,540
Even if it's something I have discarded,

649
00:30:52,620 --> 00:30:53,980
you have no right to pick it up.

650
00:30:55,140 --> 00:30:56,340
Even picking it up is a crime.

651
00:30:59,260 --> 00:31:01,220
Your arrogance and pompousness

652
00:31:01,820 --> 00:31:03,180
are truly vile.

653
00:31:04,540 --> 00:31:05,860
You look like a tiger,

654
00:31:06,140 --> 00:31:07,300
baring your fangs and claws,

655
00:31:07,940 --> 00:31:09,420
but you have nothing to back you up.

656
00:31:10,140 --> 00:31:11,020
Stop showing off here.

657
00:31:11,460 --> 00:31:13,380
I don't need you to teach me a lesson.

658
00:31:14,940 --> 00:31:15,820
Do you know?

659
00:31:17,100 --> 00:31:18,420
Qilan is actually not pregnant.

660
00:31:25,660 --> 00:31:26,540
What did you say?

661
00:31:28,100 --> 00:31:29,380
I just went to see her,

662
00:31:30,180 --> 00:31:31,620
and I discovered something.

663
00:31:34,220 --> 00:31:35,060
Consort Jiangli.

664
00:31:35,260 --> 00:31:36,100
I...

665
00:31:36,500 --> 00:31:38,060
It's fine. Go back to work.

666
00:31:38,940 --> 00:31:39,780
Yes.

667
00:31:46,660 --> 00:31:47,660
She used medicine

668
00:31:48,100 --> 00:31:49,900
to create a false pregnancy.

669
00:31:50,040 --> 00:31:50,900
Then she used medicine

670
00:31:50,900 --> 00:31:52,260
to fake a miscarriage.

671
00:31:52,940 --> 00:31:54,060
As for the blood,

672
00:31:54,580 --> 00:31:56,100
she must've calculated the timing

673
00:31:56,420 --> 00:31:57,820
and waited for her period to come

674
00:31:58,140 --> 00:31:59,220
before blaming it on you.

675
00:32:03,580 --> 00:32:04,980
I knew it.

676
00:32:06,140 --> 00:32:08,300
I had consulted with the physician
about the dosage,

677
00:32:08,940 --> 00:32:10,620
and the child would've been fine.

678
00:32:12,820 --> 00:32:13,660
You go.

679
00:32:13,940 --> 00:32:15,100
Go tell Master Jingxiu

680
00:32:15,220 --> 00:32:16,820
so he will know I was wronged.

681
00:32:16,820 --> 00:32:17,980
You go.

682
00:32:18,420 --> 00:32:19,540
You go tell Master Jingxiu.

683
00:32:19,540 --> 00:32:20,380
You go.

684
00:32:20,540 --> 00:32:21,500
It's too late now.

685
00:32:22,580 --> 00:32:23,760
She's destroyed the evidence.

686
00:32:26,260 --> 00:32:27,260
I knew it.

687
00:32:29,060 --> 00:32:30,500
You two were in cahoots

688
00:32:30,500 --> 00:32:32,220
to make a fool of me.

689
00:32:33,700 --> 00:32:35,020
I knew you wouldn't be so kind

690
00:32:35,020 --> 00:32:35,980
to visit me.

691
00:32:38,540 --> 00:32:39,700
Wait and see.

692
00:32:40,780 --> 00:32:42,420
If my father knows about this,

693
00:32:43,060 --> 00:32:44,740
he will surely plead with the Prefect.

694
00:32:45,940 --> 00:32:47,520
In just a few days, I'll be out of here.

695
00:32:47,980 --> 00:32:48,820
By then,

696
00:32:49,220 --> 00:32:50,580
I won't let you get away with it.

697
00:32:52,380 --> 00:32:53,540
You probably don't know

698
00:32:54,380 --> 00:32:56,380
that General Wang went to the Prefect,

699
00:32:57,260 --> 00:32:59,220
but the Prefect didn't change his mind.

700
00:33:01,740 --> 00:33:02,580
What did you say?

701
00:33:04,220 --> 00:33:05,580
I don't believe it.

702
00:33:06,860 --> 00:33:08,460
My father holds a lot of weight

703
00:33:08,700 --> 00:33:09,860
with the Prefect.

704
00:33:10,860 --> 00:33:12,380
With his military merits,

705
00:33:13,500 --> 00:33:15,040
the Prefect has to consider his opinion.

706
00:33:23,620 --> 00:33:24,460
Wang Danling,

707
00:33:25,340 --> 00:33:26,740
you've been treating everyone

708
00:33:27,140 --> 00:33:28,860
like pawns in your game.

709
00:33:29,980 --> 00:33:31,820
Do you really think you're a player?

710
00:33:39,380 --> 00:33:40,560
Good and evil will be repaid.

711
00:33:41,420 --> 00:33:42,420
Take care of yourself.

712
00:33:45,460 --> 00:33:47,060
Shen Jiangli!

713
00:33:47,060 --> 00:33:48,700
Come back here! Don't leave!

714
00:33:48,900 --> 00:33:50,300
Explain yourself!

715
00:33:57,700 --> 00:33:58,900
It's impossible!

716
00:34:09,580 --> 00:34:10,820
Fuling, pour me a cup of tea.

717
00:34:15,300 --> 00:34:16,140
Fuling.

718
00:34:17,420 --> 00:34:18,260
Pour me a cup of tea.

719
00:34:19,900 --> 00:34:20,740
Alright.

720
00:34:42,500 --> 00:34:44,100
My Lady, sorry.

721
00:34:45,020 --> 00:34:46,100
When I sent

722
00:34:46,300 --> 00:34:47,660
the clothes out earlier,

723
00:34:48,220 --> 00:34:49,740
I ran into Consort Jiangli.

724
00:34:50,060 --> 00:34:51,580
She saw those clothes.

725
00:34:52,060 --> 00:34:52,900
If...

726
00:34:53,820 --> 00:34:55,340
If she associates those clothes

727
00:34:55,580 --> 00:34:56,600
with something

728
00:34:56,600 --> 00:34:57,700
and discovers our secret...

729
00:34:57,700 --> 00:34:58,540
- It's fine.
- I...

730
00:35:00,940 --> 00:35:01,780
Get up.

731
00:35:07,640 --> 00:35:09,610
Even if she didn't see those clothes,

732
00:35:10,450 --> 00:35:11,660
she'd still find out about it.

733
00:35:12,940 --> 00:35:14,340
I did this

734
00:35:14,860 --> 00:35:15,900
to protect myself.

735
00:35:16,740 --> 00:35:18,100
I never intended to harm anyone.

736
00:35:19,420 --> 00:35:20,980
Wang Danling went too far,

737
00:35:20,980 --> 00:35:22,500
so I had to resort to this.

738
00:35:24,180 --> 00:35:25,180
It's fine now.

739
00:35:25,740 --> 00:35:26,620
From now on,

740
00:35:26,620 --> 00:35:27,900
we can live peacefully.

741
00:35:28,620 --> 00:35:29,940
Jiangli is wise.

742
00:35:31,130 --> 00:35:32,440
She won't interfere with matters

743
00:35:33,380 --> 00:35:34,580
that don't concern her.

744
00:35:41,140 --> 00:35:42,060
By the way, My Lady,

745
00:35:42,540 --> 00:35:43,980
your mother just sent a letter

746
00:35:43,980 --> 00:35:45,200
and said she'd come over later.

747
00:35:46,900 --> 00:35:47,940
Help me change my clothes.

748
00:35:55,620 --> 00:36:02,620
(Master Jingxiu's Mansion)

749
00:36:05,260 --> 00:36:06,260
Why are you here?

750
00:36:08,340 --> 00:36:09,180
It's getting cold,

751
00:36:09,620 --> 00:36:10,740
so I brought you a coat.

752
00:36:20,140 --> 00:36:21,300
What's happened?

753
00:36:24,140 --> 00:36:25,380
I'm just a bit sentimental.

754
00:36:26,260 --> 00:36:27,100
Wang Danling,

755
00:36:27,580 --> 00:36:29,100
as the general's lineal daughter,

756
00:36:30,700 --> 00:36:32,380
favored by all,

757
00:36:32,860 --> 00:36:34,220
grew up in the Prefect's Mansion,

758
00:36:34,220 --> 00:36:36,060
studying with the Prefect's sons,

759
00:36:36,620 --> 00:36:37,700
yet she's trapped

760
00:36:37,790 --> 00:36:39,020
in the inner chambers,

761
00:36:39,300 --> 00:36:40,380
scheming and plotting,

762
00:36:40,780 --> 00:36:41,900
hurting others and herself.

763
00:36:43,020 --> 00:36:44,140
She wants too much,

764
00:36:45,060 --> 00:36:47,580
and in the end, she's trapped
by her desires and obsessions.

765
00:36:49,140 --> 00:36:50,660
But this endless struggle

766
00:36:50,900 --> 00:36:52,380
really changes people.

767
00:36:52,960 --> 00:36:54,060
I went to see Qilan today,

768
00:36:54,230 --> 00:36:55,320
and she's changed a lot too.

769
00:36:56,020 --> 00:36:57,620
I hope she can learn from this

770
00:36:57,760 --> 00:36:59,360
and not repeat Wang Danling's mistakes.

771
00:37:00,780 --> 00:37:02,220
No matter what the situation is,

772
00:37:03,140 --> 00:37:04,300
the path is one's own choice.

773
00:37:05,270 --> 00:37:06,980
I hope that those who feel helpless

774
00:37:07,510 --> 00:37:08,780
can hold on to their true selves.

775
00:37:11,740 --> 00:37:12,580
Let's go.

776
00:37:14,740 --> 00:37:16,540
(Governance and Protection)

777
00:37:16,540 --> 00:37:17,540
By the Prefect's order,

778
00:37:17,880 --> 00:37:19,100
the guilty woman, Wang Danling,

779
00:37:19,100 --> 00:37:20,520
has plotted against Lady Shen Qilan,

780
00:37:20,820 --> 00:37:22,220
and her as the consort is revoked.

781
00:37:22,360 --> 00:37:23,960
She is to be sent to the ancestral tomb.

782
00:37:35,340 --> 00:37:38,180
(Authority)

783
00:37:41,060 --> 00:37:42,700
I invited you here today

784
00:37:42,940 --> 00:37:44,540
to express my feelings.

785
00:37:44,900 --> 00:37:45,740
I love Master Jingxiu

786
00:37:45,740 --> 00:37:47,060
for who he is,

787
00:37:47,260 --> 00:37:49,100
not for his status or wealth,

788
00:37:49,100 --> 00:37:50,380
and I won't be your enemy.

789
00:37:50,780 --> 00:37:52,620
I will always respect you and love you.

790
00:37:52,740 --> 00:37:54,100
I will never be a threat to you.

791
00:37:57,000 --> 00:38:03,680
♪Nowhere to send letters;
no news ever comes♪

792
00:38:03,780 --> 00:38:05,900
♪The night fades away♪

793
00:38:05,910 --> 00:38:07,180
My lineal daughter

794
00:38:07,660 --> 00:38:09,040
should be the most respected woman

795
00:38:09,660 --> 00:38:11,220
in Dongzhou.

796
00:38:11,860 --> 00:38:13,580
I'll give you a grand wedding

797
00:38:14,620 --> 00:38:16,460
and always stay by your side,

798
00:38:17,980 --> 00:38:19,220
shielding you from suffering.

799
00:38:19,580 --> 00:38:21,180
Once Master Jingxiu has Golden Guards

800
00:38:21,180 --> 00:38:22,400
and becomes the Young Prefect,

801
00:38:22,540 --> 00:38:24,020
you will be the most respected woman

802
00:38:24,020 --> 00:38:25,420
in Dongzhou

803
00:38:25,420 --> 00:38:26,620
after the Prefect steps down.

804
00:38:26,940 --> 00:38:28,540
That most respected position

805
00:38:29,380 --> 00:38:30,500
must be mine.

806
00:38:30,500 --> 00:38:33,080
♪Gradually disappear on the horizon♪

807
00:38:33,830 --> 00:38:39,020
♪There's only an incense stick of time
between us♪

808
00:38:39,460 --> 00:38:42,230
♪Will you remember me♪

809
00:38:42,460 --> 00:38:43,900
I lost.

810
00:38:50,180 --> 00:38:53,500
In the end, I lost.

811
00:39:10,660 --> 00:39:11,940
My Lady, Ms. Zou is here.

812
00:39:12,300 --> 00:39:13,140
Mother.

813
00:39:15,060 --> 00:39:16,340
- Sit.
- Qilan.

814
00:39:18,900 --> 00:39:20,980
Qilan, are you feeling better?

815
00:39:22,300 --> 00:39:23,580
I pity my grandson.

816
00:39:23,820 --> 00:39:25,980
Wang Danling is truly heartless.

817
00:39:26,180 --> 00:39:27,140
Mother,

818
00:39:27,140 --> 00:39:28,180
I'm fine.

819
00:39:28,900 --> 00:39:30,680
Wang Danling has gone
to the ancestral tomb,

820
00:39:30,900 --> 00:39:32,700
and Master Jingxiu has let me

821
00:39:32,700 --> 00:39:33,680
manage the household.

822
00:39:34,260 --> 00:39:35,100
Really?

823
00:39:36,780 --> 00:39:38,300
What a blessing.

824
00:39:39,730 --> 00:39:40,620
However,

825
00:39:40,620 --> 00:39:41,620
this miscarriage

826
00:39:41,620 --> 00:39:43,360
must've harmed your body.

827
00:39:43,700 --> 00:39:45,660
You must take good care of yourself,

828
00:39:45,660 --> 00:39:46,820
so you can conceive again.

829
00:39:48,420 --> 00:39:49,260
Mother,

830
00:39:49,700 --> 00:39:50,580
actually...

831
00:39:54,220 --> 00:39:55,060
What?

832
00:39:55,260 --> 00:39:56,100
You...

833
00:39:56,580 --> 00:39:57,420
Don't worry, Mother.

834
00:39:57,700 --> 00:39:58,980
No one knows about this.

835
00:39:59,300 --> 00:40:00,860
I can endure

836
00:40:00,860 --> 00:40:01,700
Wang Danling's abuse,

837
00:40:02,020 --> 00:40:03,500
but she shouldn't have humiliated you.

838
00:40:03,900 --> 00:40:05,060
On my wedding night,

839
00:40:05,460 --> 00:40:07,060
she humiliated you for no reason.

840
00:40:07,660 --> 00:40:08,700
Good child.

841
00:40:09,180 --> 00:40:10,300
It's my fault

842
00:40:10,420 --> 00:40:11,850
for letting you suffer this.

843
00:40:13,060 --> 00:40:13,900
Mother,

844
00:40:14,060 --> 00:40:15,540
now, Master Jingxiu loves me

845
00:40:15,540 --> 00:40:16,380
and trusts me.

846
00:40:16,580 --> 00:40:18,100
We'll have many good days to come.

847
00:40:20,940 --> 00:40:21,780
What's wrong?

848
00:40:23,100 --> 00:40:24,140
- What's wrong?
- Qilan,

849
00:40:24,580 --> 00:40:25,540
I'm afraid

850
00:40:25,540 --> 00:40:26,860
there won't be a future for me.

851
00:40:27,100 --> 00:40:28,220
What happened, Mother?

852
00:40:29,100 --> 00:40:31,020
I heard that your elder sister

853
00:40:31,180 --> 00:40:32,700
found the servants who used

854
00:40:32,700 --> 00:40:33,900
to serve her mother

855
00:40:34,260 --> 00:40:36,580
and said she'd investigate
her mother's death.

856
00:40:37,660 --> 00:40:38,980
Didn't her mother die of illness?

857
00:40:39,300 --> 00:40:40,700
Why investigate?

858
00:40:40,700 --> 00:40:41,540
Actually,

859
00:40:41,700 --> 00:40:43,620
there have been rumors
at home for years

860
00:40:44,020 --> 00:40:46,020
that her mother didn't die of illness.

861
00:40:47,860 --> 00:40:49,020
Mother, what do you know?

862
00:40:52,180 --> 00:40:53,580
Let her investigate.

863
00:40:55,500 --> 00:40:56,420
But...

